Andrew Arbuckle (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrew_Arbuckle_(actor) 0 Andrew Arbuckle (September 5, 1887 – September 21, 1938) was an American stage and film actor. He was the brother of Macklyn Arbuckle and cousin of Roscoe "Fatty" Arbuckle. Andrew_Arbuckle ( September_5_,_1887 – September_21_,_1938 ) was an_American_stage_and_film_actor .
